---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About · Fairness Archive" lang="en">
  <article style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 32px 96px;">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>This site documents disputed calls and governance incidents in football involving Argentina / Messi, in a fair, restrained archival register.</p>
    <h2>Three Principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Three-state distinction</strong>: every entry is tagged as "reported dispute", "called into question", or "official ruling", defaulting to "reported dispute".</li>
      <li><strong>Allegation-only wording</strong>: we state only what was reported / alleged, never framing it as a conviction.</li>
      <li><strong>Source required</strong>: each entry has at least one traceable source; responses and rulings carry sources too.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="muted">This site is not a conviction record. Criminal-level allegations are recorded only as "alleged / questioned", with the accused party's response attached.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
<style>.muted{color:var(--muted);}</style>
